Stark Says Crosslink Merges Public, Private Investing

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-04T04:29:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/stark-says-crosslink-merges-public-private-investing-video-.html
Michael Stark, founder and managing 
director of Crosslink Capital Inc., talks with Bloomberg's Kevin
Thrash about the firm's investment strategy and some of its 
company picks.  The November issue of Bloomberg Markets magazine examines 
Crosslink's investment strategy of providing venture funding for
private companies and hedge-fund investments to profit from 
public ones. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:43
 